== Cultural Properties ==

=== Gunma Prefectural Cultural Properties ===

'''Important Cultural Properties:'''
* Main Hall and Seitengū Shrine (Designated September 26, 1972)<ref>{{Cite web|ja|title=冠稲荷神社の本殿並びに聖天宮|url=https://www.city.ota.gunma.jp/page/4399.html|publisher=Ota City|accessdate=2024-08-23}}</ref>
''' Main Hall: Built in {{ill|1767|ja|享保7th year|12=draft|12=draft}}, featuring three-bay {{ill|Nagare-zukuri|ja|流造|12=draft|12=draft}} with Chidori gable and Karahafu porch.
''' Seitengū Shrine: Four-sided {{ill|Irimoya-zukuri|ja|入母屋造|12=draft|12=draft}} with Karahafu roof, built in {{ill|1857|ja|安政4th year|12=draft|12=draft}}.{{Sfn|Gunma Cultural Affairs Department|2022|pp=350-354}}<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|ja|title=冠稲荷神社を県重文に答申|url=https://www.jomo-news.co.jp/articles/-/507830|publisher=Jomo Shimbun|accessdate=2024-08-02}}</ref>

'''Natural Monuments:'''
* {{ill|Boke (Chaenomeles)|ja|ボケ|12=draft|12=draft}} Trees (Designated January 14, 1955)<ref>{{Cite web|ja|title=冠稲荷のボケ|url=https://www.city.ota.gunma.jp/page/4397.html|publisher=Ota City|accessdate=2024-08-23}}</ref>
''' Estimated to be 300–400 years old, forming dense clusters over a semicircular area. Flowers bloom in mid-March to early April.

=== Ota City Designated Cultural Properties ===

'''Intangible Cultural Properties:'''
* Hosoya Kanmuri Inari Lion Dance (Designated March 25, 1994)<ref>{{Cite web|ja|title=細谷冠稲荷の獅子舞|url=https://www.city.ota.gunma.jp/page/4496.html|publisher=Ota City|accessdate=2024-08-23}}</ref>
''' Associated with Nitta Yoshisada's ceremonial lion offering. Performed during the {{ill|Hatsuo|ja|初午|12=draft|12=draft}} Grand Festival.

== Access ==

=== By Car ===
* Located along {{ill|National Route 354|ja|国道354号|12=draft|12=draft}} Ota Bypass
* Approx. 40 minutes from {{ill|Tatebayashi IC|ja|館林インターチェンジ|12=draft|12=draft}} (Tohoku Expressway)
* Approx. 30 minutes from {{ill|Hanazono IC|ja|花園インターチェンジ|12=draft|12=draft}} (Kan-Etsu Expressway)
* Approx. 20 minutes from {{ill|Isesaki IC|ja|伊勢崎インターチェンジ|12=draft|12=draft}} (Kita-Kanto Expressway)

=== By Train ===
* {{ill|Tobu Isesaki Line|ja|東武伊勢崎線|12=draft|12=draft}}:
''' 15 minutes by taxi from {{ill|Ota Station (Gunma)|ja|太田駅|12=draft|12=draft}}
''' 20 minutes on foot from {{ill|Hosoya Station|ja|細谷駅|12=draft|12=draft}}

== Nearby Attractions ==
* {{ill|Sawano Elementary School|ja|太田市立沢野小学校|12=draft|12=draft}}
* National Historic Site: {{ill|Takayama Hikokurō Residence and Tomb|ja|高山彦九郎宅跡附遺髪塚|12=draft|12=draft}}

