* {{ill|Ōta-no-Mikoto|lt=Ōta-no-Mikoto|lt=Ōta-no-Kami|ja|太田神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōta-no-Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 太田命|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 太田命}}
