''' Main Hall: Built in {{ill|1767|ja|享保7年|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1767|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1722年|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 1722年}}[[Category:Years needing redirect replacements]], featuring three-bay [[:en:Nagare-zukuri|Nagare-zukuri]] with Chidori gable and Karahafu porch.
